aintaining hair health for the long term.&nbsp;</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-ezbkAF A-dmbO pf-131_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-brSvTw iyWbaU pf-132_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" id="blowdry" class="sc-hOGkXu eBgidd pf-133_"><a data-link="inherit" href="https://www.cliphair.co.uk/blogs/hair-blog/how-to-get-shiny-hair#Index" target="_self"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gUQvok zBuIu pf-135_">Learn How To Salon Blow Dry</span></a></h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0069/6470/7389/t/9/assets/untitled-design-12-1636105523670_500x.jpg?v=1636105526" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0069/6470/7389/t/9/assets/untitled-design-12-1636105523670.jpg?v=1636105526 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0069/6470/7389/t/9/assets/untitled-design-12-1636105523670_500x.jpg?v=1636105526 320w" width="835" height="535" sizes="(min-width: 1536px) 1536px, (min-width: 1024px) 1280px, (min-width: 640px) 768px, 320px" loading="lazy" alt="Learn How To Salon Blow Dry" data-pf-type="Image" class="sc-jQrDum igoalK pf-136_"/><p class="sc-eGPXGI dCeUID pf-137_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gUQvok zBuIu pf-139_">A salon-quality blow-out can do wonders for shiny hair. Learning salon techniques will not only feel lighter on the pocket, but your hair will thank you for it as well. Be sure to use a <a href="https://www.cliphair.co.uk/products/cliphair-heat-spray" target="_self">heat protectant spray</a> and towel dry hair evenly before applying any heat to your hair.&nbsp;</span></p><div class="sc-ezbkAF A-dmbO pf-140_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-brSvTw iyWbaU pf-141_"><p class="sc-eGPXGI dCeUID pf-142_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gUQvok zBuIu pf-144_">Divide your hair into sections and pin up the top layers. Use a paddle brush to comb through the individual sections of hair while blow-drying. Start with the bottom layers and finishing with the top.</span></p><p class="sc-eGPXGI dCeUID pf-145_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gUQvok zBuIu pf-147_">It’s not just the attachments that can be visible if the extensions are placed incorrectly, it’s also the ends. If using <a href="https://www.cliphair.co.uk/pages/clip-in-hair-extensions" target="_self">clip ins</a>, make sure to evenly spread out the larger pieces at the back so they are not all in one area. Doing this also created a <a href="https://www.cliphair.co.uk/blogs/hair-blog/layered-hair-everything-you-need-to-know-about-this-subtle-trend" target="_blank">layered effect</a> in hair which looks far more natural.&nbsp;</span></p><p class="sc-eGPXGI dCeUID pf-148_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gUQvok zBuIu pf-150_">Be sure to point the dryer downwards, blowing air in the direction of the cuticle and moving from root to tip. This will flatten and smooth the cuticle resulting in shiny hair.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-ezbkAF A-dmbO pf-151_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-brSvTw iyWbaU pf-152_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0069/6470/7389/t/9/assets/intense_hydrating_mask_500ml_jar-1636105627359_403x.jpg?v=1636105629" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0069/6470/7389/t/9/assets/intense_hydrating_mask_500ml_jar-1636105627359.jpg?v=1636105629 1536w" width="403" height="514" sizes="(min-width: 1536px) 1536px, (min-width: 1024px) 1280px, (min-width: 640px) 768px, 320px" loading="lazy" alt="Apply a Hair Mask" data-pf-type="Image" class="sc-jQrDum igoalK pf-153_"/></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-brSvTw iyWbaU pf-154_"><h2 data-pf-type="Heading" id="hairmask" class="sc-hOGkXu eBgidd pf-155_"><a data-link="inherit" href="https://www.cliphair.co.uk/blogs/hair-blog/how-to-get-shiny-hair#Index" target="_self"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gUQvok zBuIu pf-157_">Apply a Hair Mask</span></a></h2><p class="sc-eGPXGI dCeUID pf-158_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gUQvok zBuIu pf-160_">A nourishing hair mask is the gold standard of any winning hair care routine. The right mask will help to control frizz, nourish dry ends, and even prolong your hair colour, allowing it to look glossy and healthy for longer.</span></p><p class="sc-eGPXGI dCeUID pf-161_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gUQvok zBuIu pf-163_">Shiny Hair Mask? <br>Try Moroccanoil: Intense Hydrating Mask.<br>We love this argan oil-based hair mask. Argan oil is known to be full of antioxidants, vitamin E, minerals, and fatty acids, that help restore shine and smoothness to hair. It’s meant for medium to thick hair.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-ezbkAF A-dmbO pf-164_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-brSvTw iyWbaU pf-165_"><h2 data-pf-type="Heading" id="shampoo" class="sc-hOGkXu eBgidd pf-166_"><a data-link="inherit" href="https://www.cliphair.co.uk/blogs/hair-blog/how-to-get-shiny-hair#Index" target="_self"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gUQvok zBuIu pf-168_">Use a Deep Cleansing Shampoo</span></a></h2><p class="sc-eGPXGI dCeUID pf-169_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gUQvok zBuIu pf-171_">After a few days of styling, product buildup can transform your locks from luscious to lackluster. Try using a deep cleansing shampoo at least once a week to regenerate your tresses and boost shine.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-ezbkAF A-dmbO pf-172_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="p